le=Scott Rosenberg & Jeff Pinkner To Write ‘Jumanji: Welcome To The Jungle’ Sequel|first=Mike|last=Fleming, Jr.|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2018-02-06|accessdate=2018-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207134809/http://deadline.com/2018/02/jumanji-welcome-to-the-jungle-sequel-scott-rosenberg-jeff-pinkner-sony-dwayne-johnson-kevin-hart-jack-black-1202278493/|archive-date=2018-02-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

